	:::warning
	Passing `NaN`, infinity, or a number less than 1/60 is equivalent to passing 1/60.
	:::

	```lua
		Promise.delay(5):andThenCall(print, "This prints after 5 seconds")
	```

	@function delay
	@within Promise
	@param seconds number
	@return Promise<number>
]=]
